THE APPLESOFT KEYWORD CODES PROGRAMWILL ALLOW YOU TO SEE THE TOKENVALUES  OF EVERY APPLESOFT KEYWORDWITH AN      AMPERSAND COMMAND.FOR EXAMPLE; TYPING THIS:    &PRINT...WILL PRINT OUT THE VALUE OF THE'PRINT' KEYWORD IN HEX.  THIS VALUEIS  THE VALUE STORED INTERNALLY TOREPRESENTTHE APPLESOFT 'PRINT'STATEMENT.